summary: An Ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit for the laying off, widening, altering, extending and establishing of Western Avenue, from Eagle Street to Fourth Avenue West, and Elliott Avenue; and for the changing and establishing of the curb grades of said Western Avenue and other streets and avenues, and for the grading and regrading of said streets and avenues and approaches thereto, all as provided under Ordinance No. 30864, Cause No. 97084, and authorizing the payment of all taxable costs incurred by the owners of said property in said condemnation proceedings, and appropriating money therefor.
